manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Gentle Cleansing Made with gentle ingredients so you can clean your baby’s bottom as well as their delicate face Top to Bottoms Cleaning Babies are just as messy as they are sweet, and Pampers wipes are made to wipe everything from faces to hands to high chairs as well as bottoms Baby Fresh Scent Available in our beloved Baby Fresh scent for a refreshing clean​ Fragrance Free Available unscented and fragrance-free for delicate skin Pair with Baby-Dry Diapers To help keep your baby’s skin dry and healthy, we recommend pairing Pampers wipes with Pampers Baby-Dry diapers with LockAway Channels for up to 12 hours of overnight dryness

Our Commitment Caring for babies is in our DNA. Our Pampers Bright Beginnings programs enable healthy development and early success for babies and families through education, hospital partnerships, and donations March of Dimes Partnership Pampers is proud to support the March of Dimes in giving every baby a fighting chance. We help provide our smallest diapers to the 1 million babies born before 28-week gestational age each year Sustainability Pampers cares for every baby and the planet they grow up in. We maintain zero manufacturing to landfill across all our plants and are committed to 100% renewable electricity by 2030 Community Donations Through ongoing donation efforts and partnerships with organizations like Feeding America and Matthew 25, Pampers strives to help babies get the bright beginnings they deserve Changing Table Access 9 out of 10 dads have used a public restroom that lacks a changing table. As part of our “Love the Change” campaign, we’re providing 5,000 changing tables for men’s restrooms across North America Hospital Support Proud to be the #1 choice of U.S. hospitals for nearly 50 years, we partner with nurses to develop skin-protecting products and support nursing education—all to help baby’s healthy development

Are Pampers wipes gentle and durable? Yes! Pampers Wipes are 4x stronger vs. the leading U.S. sub-brand and clean and wipe away germs! Our product helps maintain skin’s natural pH. Are Pampers wipes safe for my baby? Yes! Babies' health and safety are our first priority at Pampers, which is why our products are hypoallergenic and free of parabens and latex. Our wipes are thoroughly tested to make sure they are safe for your baby and baby’s skin. Are these wipes flushable? No. Our baby wipes are not designed to be flushed. How do I open the refill pack? Open at the seam on either side of the refill pack and insert the stack of wipes into your wipes tub. Do Pampers wipes come with a pop-top? Yes! This Baby-Clean multi-pack comes with 8 Pop-Top packs and 8 refill packs, for inserting into a wipes tub.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Terrific wipes at a fantastic price
reviews.reviewText: Can't go wrong with these. Strong, pop up easily one at a time not in clumps, large enough, stay moist, love the aloe & vitamin e protection (soft!). I was hoping for the original "Johnson & Johnson baby powder" smell or the original Pampers' scent (both from the early 70's) but the scent in these is really mild and quite pleasant.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Baby Softness Delivered: Pampers Baby Fresh Scented Baby Wipes - 72 Count
reviews.reviewText: Ah, behold the gateway to baby bliss – Pampers Baby Fresh Scented Baby Wipes. It's like a delicate cloud of happiness, wrapped in 72 soft, moist wipes designed to make both baby and parent sigh in relief.The scent is like a gentle whisper of freshness, like a meadow after a light rain. It's not overpowering; it's a subtle embrace that accompanies every wipe, ensuring a clean and pleasant experience.Each wipe is like a soft cuddle for your baby's delicate skin. It glides smoothly, tenderly embracing even the tiniest creases and folds. It's like a comforting hug for your little one during those precious diaper-changing moments.The pack of 72 wipes is like having a portable oasis of cleanliness. Whether you're at home, on the go, or in the middle of a baby-pocalypse, these wipes are your trusty sidekick, ready to tackle any mess life throws your way.In summary: Pampers Baby Fresh Scented Baby Wipes, a fragrance of joy for both baby and parent. It's like the whisper of a gentle breeze on your baby's skin, bringing smiles and comfort with every wipe. Embrace the softness, embrace the freshness!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Never using any other ones for my kids
reviews.reviewText: We've used parents choice wipes sense our son was a newborn and we just tried these. There absolutely amazing. Will be buying these in bulk from here on out. Smell amazing and left our sons bum super clean with no residue like other brands.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 10, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I love pampers wipes especially the baby clean scent they are so soft and smell so good and has never caused irritation on my baby’s skin. I have looked all over for a good deal on these and this is one of the best prices I’ve found and they get to my house so quickly!

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Came on time !
reviews.reviewText: Diapers are great quality and also affordable! Wipes were a great price to for how many came in the box . Both came in a huge box together

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Works good enough
reviews.reviewText: These wipes work well enough, but are more like wet fabric softner sheets for a dryer. They clean things good enough, but are really thin and overpowering with the scent.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 12, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Durable soft wet enough for poop diapers cleans well

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 14, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great wipes in mega value box
reviews.reviewText: Gift to my sister in law for second baby. I had bought myself a box and knew these would be wonderful for her too. It took me quite some time to use them all.

reviews.reviewTitle: No las uses si tu bebé está rosado
reviews.reviewText: Son delgadas, pero resistentes, tienen aroma fuerte, pero no es molesto. Lo que si deben tener cuidado es que si las usan para limpiar a su bebé y está rosado le va a arder, lo sé porque yo me limpie mis manos y tenía una cortada y me ardio. Las compré para desinfectar los juguetes del bebé y limpiarlo a él pero cuando no está rosado.
